<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>429: Too Many Requests - Kuppa.js</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #ffffff;
            --fg: #000000;
            --gray: #666666;
            --line: #eaeaea;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            :root {
                --bg: #000000;
                --fg: #ffffff;
                --gray: #888888;
                --line: #333333;
            }
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--fg);
            font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 0;
            padding-right: 23px;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
            line-height: 49px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .message-box {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: left;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 20px;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--fg);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin: 4px 0 0 0;
            color: var(--gray);
            max-width: 320px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: var(--gray);
        }

        .brand {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--fg);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>429</h1>
        <div class="message-box">
            <h2>Too many requests.</h2>
            <p>The Kuppa Shield has throttled your connection to protect the engine. Please try again in a minute.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        Powered by <span class="brand">kuppa.js</span>
    </div>
</body>
</html>